HEADWORD: Susurration
<hw>Su`sur*ra"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>susurratio</ets>, fr. <ets>susurrare</ets> to whisper: cf. F.
<ets>susurration</ets>.]</ety> <def>A whispering; a soft murmur.</def>
